### Movie Recommendation API - Sample HTTP Requests (.http)

#### 1. User Registration

```
POST http://localhost:8000/api/user_register/
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

username=yourusername&password=yourpassword&first_name=Gopika&last_name=Das&email=gopika@example.com&bio=I love movies&age=22
```

#### 2. Login

```
POST http://localhost:8000/api/login/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "yourusername",
    "password": "yourpassword"
}
```

#### 3. Get Profile

```
GET http://localhost:8000/api/profile/
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
```

#### 4. Search Movies

```
GET http://localhost:8000/api/search/?q=inception
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
```

#### 5. List All Movies

```
GET http://localhost:8000/api/movies/
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
```

#### 6. Get Single Movie

```
GET http://localhost:8000/api/single/1
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
```

#### 7. Add Movie (Admin Only)

```
POST http://localhost:8000/api/add_movie/
Authorization: Bearer <admin_access_token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "movie_title": "Inception",
    "description": "A thief steals corporate secrets using dream-sharing technology.",
    "genres_id": [1, 2],
    "director": "Christopher Nolan",
    "released_at": "2010-07-16",
    "duration": 148,
    "poster_url": "https://example.com/poster.jpg",
    "trailer_url": "https://youtube.com/watch?v=YoHD9XEInc0",
    "rating": 4.8
}
```

#### 8. Update Movie (Admin Only)

```
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/update/1
Authorization: Bearer <admin_access_token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "rating": 4.9
}
```

#### 9. Delete Movie (Admin Only)

```
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/delete/1
Authorization: Bearer <admin_access_token>
```

#### 10. Add Review

```
POST http://localhost:8000/api/add_review/1
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Amazing Movie",
    "comment": "Really enjoyed the plot and acting!",
    "rating": 5
}
```

#### 11. Update Review

```
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/update_review/1
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "rating": 4.5
}
```

#### 12. Delete Review

```
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/delete_review/1
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
```

#### 13. List Reviews for a Movie

```
GET http://localhost:8000/api/list_movie_review/1
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
```

#### 14. Mark Movie as Watched

```
POST http://localhost:8000/api/watchedmovies/
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "movie_id": 1
}
```

#### 15. Get Recommended Movies

```
GET http://localhost:8000/api/movies/recommended/
Authorization: Bearer <access_token>
```
